=== Negative - Olumsuz ===
Negative verb stem (verb-me/ma-), auxiliary consonant ''y'' (it is used to establish a connection between two vowels),  the suffixes -ecek or -acak (according to the vowel harmony) and the personal ending are added to the verb stem. The "k" in the suffixes become a "ğ" before the 1st personal endings:
{{Turkish/Box||{{turkish/c|Verb stem}} + appropriate form of {{tr/suff|me|dash=no}} + buffer letter {{tr/suff|y}} + appropriate form of {{turkish/Suffix|ecek|dash=no}} + {{turkish/c|personal ending}}}}
{| width="100%"
|width=50%|
<!--Table 1-->
{| {{Turkish/Table|width=100%|verb inflection • [[Turkish/Future Tense|future tense]] |{{tr/word|gel|to come}}|columns=4}}
!colspan=4 style="text-align:center"| {{tr/word|gelmemek|not to come}}
|-
! {{tr/word|ben|color=purple}} {{tr/word|gel|come}}{{tr/suff|me|color=#CD0000|dash=no}}{{tr/suff|y|dash=no}}{{tr/suff|eceğ|color=b|dash=no}}{{tr/suff|im|color=purple|dash=no}}
| I will not come
! {{tr/word|biz|color=purple}} {{tr/word|gel|come}}{{tr/suff|me|color=#CD0000|dash=no}}{{tr/suff|y|dash=no}}{{tr/suff|eceğ|color=b|dash=no}}{{tr/suff|iz|color=purple|dash=no}}
| we will not come
|-
! {{tr/word|sen|color=purple}} {{tr/word|gel|come}}{{tr/suff|me|color=#CD0000|dash=no}}{{tr/suff|y|dash=no}}{{tr/suff|ecek|color=b|dash=no}}{{tr/suff|sin|color=purple|dash=no}}
| you will not come
! {{tr/word|siz|color=purple}} {{tr/word|gel|come}}{{tr/suff|me|color=#CD0000|dash=no}}{{tr/suff|y|dash=no}}{{tr/suff|ecek|color=b|dash=no}}{{tr/suff|siniz|color=purple|dash=no}}
| you will not come
|-
