| he/she/it will not come
! {{tr/word|onlar|color=purple}} {{tr/word|gel|come}}{{tr/suff|me|color=#CD0000|dash=no}}{{tr/suff|y|dash=no}}{{tr/suff|ecek|color=b|dash=no}}{{tr/suff|ler|color=purple|dash=no}}
