! {{tr/word|o|color=purple}} {{tr/word|gel|come}}{{tr/suff|ecek|color=b|dash=no}}&nbsp;{{tr/suff|mi|dash=no|color=no}}{{tr/suff||color=purple|dash=no}}
| will he/she/it come
! {{tr/word|onlar|color=purple}} {{tr/word|gel|come}}{{tr/suff|ecek|color=b|dash=no}}{{tr/suff|ler|color=purple|dash=no}} {{tr/suff|mi|dash=no|color=no}}
